<doc id="658997" wikidata="Q863437" url="?curid=658997" title="Montreuil-en-Auge">
<text>Montreuil-en-Auge (, literally &quot;Montreuil in Auge&quot;) is a commune in the department of Calvados in the Normandy region in northwestern France.

