<doc id="659079" wikidata="Q863078" url="?curid=659079" title="Les Moutiers-en-Auge">
<text>Les Moutiers-en-Auge (, literally &quot;Les Moutiers in Auge&quot;) is a commune in the department of Calvados in the Normandy region in northwestern France.

Les Moutiers-en-Auge is located at the junction of the D90 and D249 departmental roads.

==Population==

